{"tid":2056533,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[時光機]一齊貼你上年6月9日反送中遊行影嘅相","createTime":"2020-06-08T18:20:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-09T04:05:40.000Z","uid":1938,"like":18,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"3cee61f64a3f9e8392981028c00c2d7861e4a7c0","tid":2056533,"uid":1938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T18:20:54.000Z","msg":"嗰日約咗朋友2:30pm去天后站等<br />\n警方仲話估計應該有3萬人<br />\n但1點左右個whatsapp已經不停收到各種交通資訊<br />\n好多站都已經唔俾人再入/封咗好多出口<br />\n街上面嘅人全部都係着白色衫 睇到我起哂雞皮<br />\n<br />\n最後我根本去唔到天后 要轉東涌綫過海<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BNmr0iZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBNmr0iZ.jpg&h=fe64c682&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n最後4點先迫到入維園<br />\n撞到好撚多n年冇見過嘅舊同學/朋友仔<br />\n嗰陣叫口號仲係叫林鄭下台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/46yBC7S.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F46yBC7S.jpg&h=93ebb353&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QVdmPe3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQVdmPe3.jpg&h=5263ecea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bbZxbtC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbbZxbtC.jpg&h=1b401208&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後行到去金鐘<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Rr6WC8S.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRr6WC8S.jpg&h=d82f0328&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n勿相認<br />\n<br />\n希望睇返呢d相<br />\n大家會記得自己當初肯行出嚟<br />\n就係因為想改變"},{"pid":"7e68b9ab4ebc2774f2606e8fba21bb03b07e90ac","tid":2056533,"uid":1938,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T18:21:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/es6vHBV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fes6vHBV.jpg&h=593dd816&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0178bdbfc2bdb344011d6b3dd8958cf9d1c65979","tid":2056533,"uid":1938,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"c